snippet.title: Gothic 3 Gameplay [HD]
snippet.description:
Some random gameplay of Gothic 3, which is, in my oppinion still one of the better RPG's out there. The gameplay shown in this video is recorded around level 4, which is about 4 hours into the game. 

All settings are maxed. There are some framerate issues when recording..Fraps cuts my fps into half. 

Feel free to ask any questions!
